message.body: I think this week's crappy Wednesday weather may cancel our walk.
Yeah, I was wondering. This sucks :(
Indeed it does! We can see how things look later today but I'm feeling like a drowned rat this morning.
Me too. Alternate idea: want to come over and watch the flyers? We can order food
Game is at 7. Want to come over around 6:45 so we can order some food? I'm sure it'll take a while to come on a night like this
Sounds good. Where are u thinking o ordering from? I never order food so I'm leaving this up to you.
Anything is fine with me. Tons of options. I'll pull up grubhub and we can look through menus when you get here :)
Awesome! You always show me new stuff!
